ds" class="mw-redirect" title="New No Limit Records">The New No Limit</a>, <a href="/wiki/Universal_Records_(defunct_record_label)" class="mw-redirect" title="Universal Records (defunct record label)">Universal</a>, <a href="/wiki/Body_Head_Entertainment" class="mw-redirect" title="Body Head Entertainment">Body Head</a> (Former)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row"><span class="nowrap">Associated acts</span></th><td><a href="/wiki/504_Boyz" title="504 Boyz">504 Boyz</a>, <a href="/wiki/Body_Head_Bangerz" title="Body Head Bangerz">Body Head Bangerz</a>, <a href="/wiki/Master_P" title="Master P">Master P</a>, <a href="/wiki/Magic_(rapper)" title="Magic (rapper)">Magic</a>, <a href="/wiki/Baby_Boy_da_Prince" title="Baby Boy da Prince">Baby Boy da Prince</a>, Lil' Brittany</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><b>Darwin Turner</b> (born October 29, 1980), better known by his <a href="/wiki/Stage_name" title="Stage name">stage name</a> <b>Choppa</b>, is an American <a href="/wiki/Rapper" class="mw-redirect" title="Rapper">rapper</a> and <a href="/wiki/Songwriter" title="Songwriter">songwriter</a>.
</p>
